title: My Journey to the Afterlife - Best of Coast to Coast AM - 5/6/20

description:
George Noory and artist David Ditchfield recount the accident where his arm was severed after he was dragged under a train, how he met strange spiritual beings when he died at the hospital, and amazing new talents he gained after returning to this world.
